casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Azmar CARTER, Defendant-Petitioner. M-522 September Term 2018
081493 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 8, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion of the American Civil Liberties Union of New Jersey for leave to file a brief and argue as amicus curiae is granted. Oral argument is limited to five minutes.
